8
00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:49.929
Jeff D'Andria: is very good to call out. Whenever you've kind of gone above and beyond in some context, because I'm going to guess it's more rare, say, to be in that… finishing in 3, so you're going kind of above and beyond, feel free… really important to, like, call things like that out.

